ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#42: FILE: fs/unionfs/file.c:27:
+	if (unlikely((err = unionfs_file_revalidate(file, false))))

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

